===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# {{transitive}} To [[declare]] [[openly]] and [[boldly]], as something believed to be right; to [[own]], [[acknowledge]] or [[confess]] [[frankly]].
# {{transitive}} To [[state]] in a [[positive]] manner.

